author: Russell Brand
description: LIVE at the Student Action Summit, I’m joining TPUSA to explore the real forces shaping our world. Who holds the power? Can we return it to the people? And what possibilities lie ahead if we choose truth, unity, and decentralization? Join me as we question the narratives, challenge the establishment, and imagine a free future together.
title: LIVE at Student Action Summit - Let’s Talk Power, People, and Possibility!

author: Russell Brand
description:
Charlie Kirk says Trump is being pressured to abandon his immigration promises—and he’s not the only one who thinks so. Is the migrant issue just a distraction from the real power behind the problem: Big Agriculture, Hospitality, and Corporate America? Today I unpack the lobbying pressure Trump is facing, and why some say ICE raids are theatre while the industries fuelling illegal immigration remain untouched. Is Trump making the same compromises as everyone else in Washington? Or is this the moment we find out who really runs the show? Let me know what you think in the comments and chat.
